#~ "your play level and track your "
#~ "progress over time using the positions"
#~ " imported in the database. It "
#~ "computes and displays **PR** (Performance "
#~ "Rate) and **MWC cost** (Match Winning"
#~ " Chance cost) for all positions or"
#~ " a filtered subset."

